00:59:44,581 --> 00:59:48,642
Bertha, you've no idea
how beautiful Monte Carlo is

811
00:59:48,751 --> 00:59:51,083
The park- simply divine

812
00:59:51,187 --> 00:59:54,122
And the promenade -
like a walk in the clouds

813
00:59:54,223 --> 00:59:58,489
