Yes Quite right Quite right

819
01:00:14,210 --> 01:00:16,144
A very strong sea breeze

820
01:00:16,245 --> 01:00:19,305
And when the countess felt so cold?

821
01:00:19,415 --> 01:00:23,408
Well, uh, finally I became so -

