01:06:33,723 --> 01:06:35,691
[ Sighs ]

880
01:06:45,267 --> 01:06:47,235
Oh, where -

881
01:06:51,140 --> 01:06:53,108
Oh!

882
01:06:53,209 --> 01:06:56,110
Oh, the key

883
01:06:59,048 --> 01:07:01,744
<i>just a moment, please</i>

884
01:07:07,590 --> 01:07:09,558
[ Murmurs ]

