making me nervous?

992
01:15:23,385 --> 01:15:25,444
You know I can't go
until my hair is dressed

993
01:15:25,554 --> 01:15:27,579
But, darling, you look
so beautiful the way it is

994
01:15:27,689 --> 01:15:31,056
